// Wire contract for the kubebolt-agent ↔ backend bidi channel (Sprint A.5).
//
// Replaces the v1 AgentIngest service (Register / StreamMetrics / Heartbeat)
// with a single bidi RPC that multiplexes ALL traffic — handshake, metrics,
// heartbeat, and the K8s API proxy (kube_request / kube_response /
// kube_event). The proxy is what enables SaaS multi-cluster: the backend
// runs outside the customer's cluster and reaches the apiserver through
// the agent's persistent outbound stream.
//
// Migration: hard cutover from v1. The agent and backend in this branch
